name: Original One of a Kind Artist Card "Remember" Handmade Collage ACEO
description:
Original floral themed artist card, entitled "Remember". This collaged card was made with vintage greeting card illustration, tissue paper, rub ons and stickers, on a cardstock/scrapbook paper base. Titled, stamped and dated on the back by the artist (hey, that's me!).

Card measures 3.5" x 2.5".
